Email Application Project Use case

Scenario: As an IT Support Administration specialist and assigned with 
		  the task of creating email accounts for new hires.

The application is expected to do the following:
	- Generate an email with the following syntax: firstname.lastname@department.company.com
	- Determine the department(Sales, development, accounting), if none leave blank
	- Generate a random String for a password
	- Have set methods to change the password, set the mailbox capacity, and define an alternative email address
	- Have get methods to display the name, email, and mailbox capacity